<button onClick={() => setCount(count + 1)}>
  Increment
</button>
```

ğŸ“Œ Only text node updates, not full page

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ§  Common Misconceptions

âŒ Virtual DOM replaces Real DOM
âŒ React updates entire DOM

âœ… React updates **only changed parts**

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

âŒ Common Beginner Mistakes

* Not using keys in lists
* Using index as key
* Expecting instant DOM changes
* Mutating state directly

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ’¡ Best Practices

* Always use unique keys
* Keep components small
* Avoid unnecessary re-renders
* Use state wisely
* Trust Reactâ€™s rendering

